data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom brick ranch located in Mount Washington. Sitting an approximately 1 acre, you will have plenty of room for the kids to play. Large two car detached garage with an additional lean to. Many updates throughout. Newer roof on both house and garage. Newer heating and air and stainless appliances. Schedule your showing today.
